  • Method Details

    • verify

      public static ItemStackWrapper verify(net.minecraft.world.item.ItemStack itemStack)
      Checks whether the given ItemStack is null, empty. If it is, returns air. If it isn't, returns a new ItemStack for that item.
      Parameters:
      itemStack - The ItemStack to check if it's a valid stack.
      Returns:
      Null if the stack was invalid, or a wrapper for the stack if it was valid.
